title: 223.3 VOX MIni - The Panhead Strikes Back
description:
A new mini episode is out! So many different questions, so little time...but we try!

We talk Trump, the band Skillet, the deconstruction of the Church, and a suggestion that maybe some people want to have a few tiers on Patreon to be named after Taylor Swift.

Also, Mike is still wearing all black. üò¨üòê
